<SiteLayout site="siliconbased" title="What are WebSockets? Real-time web explained" description="A complete guide to WebSockets, real-time bidirectional communication, and how they compare to Server-Sent Events (SSE) and long polling." canonical="https://siliconbased.dev/what-is-websocket" schema={schema}>
